      "text": "A quantum system will be said to be controllable by fully quantum feedback if there is some initial state for the controller (possibly entangled with the state of another quantum system), a sequence of interactions with the controller and a sequence of applied semiclassical potentials that takes the system from some initial state r to a desired final state rd which can also be entangled with another quantum system."
